1
00:00:12,790 --> 00:00:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? This is Nishino.</font>

2
00:00:15,110 --> 00:00:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the To-Ou Medical 
University Hospital.</i></font>

3
00:00:17,030 --> 00:00:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your family member, Tsuyoshi Nishino-san, 
has been hospitalized.</i></font>

4
00:00:20,810 --> 00:00:22,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

5
00:00:22,010 --> 00:00:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's currently being examined 
and treated here at the hospital.</i></font>

6
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we're calling to ask that a 
family member come to the hospital</i></font>

7
00:00:28,810 --> 00:00:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so we can explain the patient's condition 
and discuss future treatment options.</i></font>

8
00:00:32,510 --> 00:00:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#d59199">Emergency Entrance</font></font>

9
00:00:39,940 --> 00:00:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san!</font>

10
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir! Can you hear me?</font>

11
00:00:43,020 --> 00:00:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in the hospital.</font>

12
00:00:44,210 --> 00:00:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything will be all right.</font>

13
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kashiwagi. Do you know him?</font>

14
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

15
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please put me on your team, Sensei.</font>

16
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#d59199">Emergency Entrance</font></font>

17
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'm Mizuho Nishino.</font>

18
00:02:31,350 --> 00:02:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I received a call saying my
father's been hospitalized here.</font>

19
00:02:31,350 --> 00:02:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="16"><b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#8d878f">Emergency Room Reception</font></font></b></font></font>

20
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wait a moment.</font>

21
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho!</font>

22
00:02:39,010 --> 00:02:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin!</font>

23
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness I caught you 
before the surgery.</font>

24
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin, how's my dad?</font>

25
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's stable.</font>

26
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be better once 
we perform the surgery.</font>

27
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

28
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. Don't worry.</font>

29
00:02:56,870 --> 00:03:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was added to the treatment team 
and will be there during the operation.</font>

30
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will?</font>

31
00:03:04,010 --> 00:03:06,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you think I became 
a doctor in the first place?</font>

32
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin!</font>

33
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I entrust my father to you.</font>

34
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've worked relentlessly since that day.</i></font>

35
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not who I was back then.</i></font>

36
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now... I can help her.</i></font>

37
00:04:00,510 --> 00:04:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not letting Mizuho go 
through those feelings again.</i></font>

38
00:04:04,790 --> 00:04:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mom... Please save Dad...</i></font>

39
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f5f5f5"><font size="20">Airu</font></font></font></font>

40
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f5f5f5"><font size="10">Incoming call...</font></font></font></font>

41
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Airu? Why are you calling so suddenly?</font>

42
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I heard from Syugo! Is your dad okay?</i></font>

43
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's in surgery right now...</font>

44
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm waiting for them to finish.</i></font>

45
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho... How are you doing?</font>

46
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I can't be by your side.</font>

47
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's okay.</i></font>

48
00:04:34,710 --> 00:04:37,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm feeling relieved 
just hearing your voice.</i></font>

49
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank you.</i></font>

50
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have delayed my return to London.</font>

51
00:04:42,910 --> 00:04:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

52
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you alone right now?</font>

53
00:04:47,180 --> 00:04:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah...</i></font>

54
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so frazzled... I was only 
able to contact Syugo about this.</font>

55
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

56
00:04:54,660 --> 00:04:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what about Shin?</font>

57
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're at Shin's hospital, right?</font>

58
00:04:58,410 --> 00:05:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I am. Shin's able to be in the 
operating room with my dad.</i></font>

59
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so? Then that's a relief.</font>

60
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

61
00:05:07,370 --> 00:05:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We of all people know
how great Shin-chan is.</i></font>

62
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right?</i></font>

63
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gonna be okay. Don't worry.</font>

64
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You're right.</font>

65
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have faith and wait.</font>

66
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks, Airu.</i></font>

67
00:05:25,710 --> 00:05:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

68
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:28,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

69
00:05:28,770 --> 00:05:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f8f7f9">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

70
00:05:28,770 --> 00:05:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#727169">Syugo</font></font>

71
00:05:28,770 --> 00:05:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f8f7f9">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

72
00:05:28,770 --> 00:05:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#727169">{\an7}<font size="16">I contacted Kizuki, too. 
But he hasn't responded.
 He might be at practice.</font></font></font>

73
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I contacted Kizuki, too. 
But he hasn't responded.</i></font>

74
00:05:31,010 --> 00:05:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He might be at practice.</i></font>

75
00:05:34,090 --> 00:05:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh. That swimming-obsessed idiot.</font>

76
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your best, Shin-chan.</font>

77
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I leave the rest to you.</font>

78
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

79
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work, Kashiwagi.</font>

80
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

81
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank god.</i></font>

82
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'll be okay...</i></font>

83
00:06:18,490 --> 00:06:20,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so glad that he'll be okay.</i></font>

84
00:06:23,780 --> 00:06:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin!</font>

85
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to tell you 
that the surgery's complete.</font>

86
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a success.</font>

87
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness...</font>

88
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's still asleep from the anesthesia.</font>

89
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he should be awake 
by tomorrow afternoon.</font>

90
00:06:39,090 --> 00:06:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

91
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be better in no time.</font>

92
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

93
00:06:47,210 --> 00:06:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for saving my dad.</font>

94
00:06:52,930 --> 00:06:54,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho. Do you have some time?</font>

95
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:55,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

96
00:06:56,610 --> 00:07:00,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... There's something 
I need to tell you.</font>

97
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f5f5f5"><font size="20">Kizuki</font></font></font></font>

98
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#f5f5f5"><font size="10">Incoming call...</font></font></font></font>

99
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#7e7993">Emergency Entrance</font></font>

100
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:10,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki!</font>

101
00:07:11,490 --> 00:07:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I couldn't come sooner.</font>

102
00:07:13,380 --> 00:07:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just heard the voicemail 
Syugo left me...</font>

103
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came all the way to the hospital 
after hearing that?</font>

104
00:07:19,170 --> 00:07:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I was worried about you.</font>

105
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could have at least 
used an umbrella...</font>

106
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But thanks.</font>

107
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... How's your dad?</font>

108
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His heart surgery was successful.</font>

109
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just need to monitor him 
for the next few days.</font>

110
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need to worry now.</font>

111
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. I'm glad.</font>

112
00:07:40,010 --> 00:07:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of you, Shin.</font>

113
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

114
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure my dad would be surprised to 
hear that Shin took part in his surgery.</font>

115
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going home, Mizuho? 
I can take you.</font>

116
00:07:53,490 --> 00:07:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I was thinking of staying by Dad's 
side until he regains consciousness.</font>

117
00:07:58,450 --> 00:07:59,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I can stay with you.</font>

118
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:02,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only family members can be in the ICU.</font>

119
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll drop Mizuho off at her house later.</font>

120
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should go home.</font>

121
00:08:09,220 --> 00:08:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll catch a cold if you stay like that.</font>

122
00:08:13,660 --> 00:08:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san.</font>

123
00:08:15,970 --> 00:08:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

124
00:08:16,910 --> 00:08:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to interrupt you.</font>

125
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There're a few things we need to explain</font>

126
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">regarding your father's 
hospitalization paperwork.</font>

127
00:08:23,110 --> 00:08:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for that. I'll be right there.</font>

128
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for coming, Kizuki.</font>

129
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dad and I will be fine now.</font>

130
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

131
00:08:33,070 --> 00:08:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me know if there's 
anything I can help you with.</font>

132
00:08:36,250 --> 00:08:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see you later, Mizuho.</font>

133
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh. Thanks again, Shin.</font>

134
00:08:43,770 --> 00:08:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad Mizuho's not crying.</font>

135
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just don't know about it.</font>

136
00:08:54,930 --> 00:08:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm leaving Mizuho 
and her dad in your care.</font>

137
00:08:57,210 --> 00:08:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

138
00:08:58,060 --> 00:09:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki. I'd never let Mizuho cry.</font>

139
00:09:04,930 --> 00:09:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nor would I ever make her worry.</font>

140
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll use my own ways to make her happy.</font>

141
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. But...</font>

142
00:09:13,570 --> 00:09:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't lose to you when it comes 
to wanting Mizuho to be happy.</font>

143
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez... Sorry to worry you two.</font>

144
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't a laughing matter, Dad!</font>

145
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really scared us!</font>

146
00:09:39,060 --> 00:09:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, sorry.</font>

147
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll check on you 
for two to three weeks.</font>

148
00:09:42,490 --> 00:09:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If nothing else arises, 
you can be released.</font>

149
00:09:45,110 --> 00:09:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Shin-kun.</font>

150
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never thought I'd see the day
 you'd be the one to save me.</font>

151
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin was very dependable, you know?</font>

152
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right.</font>

153
00:09:58,020 --> 00:10:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to call everyone real quick.</font>

154
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

155
00:10:06,730 --> 00:10:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir.</font>

156
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

157
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember what 
I told you in the past?</font>

158
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

159
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a doctor, just like I said I'd be.</font>

160
00:10:16,930 --> 00:10:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...?</font>

161
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I become a doctor in the future...</font>

162
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">Can I propose to Mizuho?</font></font>

163
00:10:28,350 --> 00:10:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin-kun?!</font>

164
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, please rest up
 for the next few days.</font>

165
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:41,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I rest up after that?</font>

166
00:10:45,190 --> 00:10:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

167
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

168
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to tell you something, Shin.</font>

169
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry I'm late.</font>

170
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay.</font>

171
00:11:05,210 --> 00:11:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything okay at work?</font>

172
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Anyway, here.</font>

173
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! A fruit sandwich!</font>

174
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not the ones 
from the Enoki store, though.</font>

175
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't eaten anything 
since yesterday, right?</font>

176
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll get carsick if you don't eat.</font>

177
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Shin!</font>

178
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't mind if I do!</font>

179
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:30,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yummy!</font>

180
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is just what I needed 
for my weary bones.</font>

181
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're exaggerating.</font>

182
00:11:35,970 --> 00:11:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kashiwagi-sensei! 
Are you going home already?</font>

183
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei! Who's this?</font>

184
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your girlfriend?</font>

185
00:11:42,410 --> 00:11:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! No!</font>

186
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin-sensei is <i>my</i> boyfriend!</font>

187
00:11:47,890 --> 00:11:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? Sensei?</font>

188
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever you say.</font>

189
00:11:54,230 --> 00:11:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you feel better, 
but don't run around too much.</font>

190
00:11:57,740 --> 00:11:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, but...</font>

191
00:12:02,830 --> 00:12:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A paper airplane?</font>

192
00:12:04,620 --> 00:12:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one won't fly at all.</font>

193
00:12:07,810 --> 00:12:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm making it fly by running.</font>

194
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Mizuho. 
Can you wait a little bit longer?</font>

195
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

196
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to teach them 
how to make a paper airplane.</font>

197
00:12:19,020 --> 00:12:20,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

198
00:12:24,530 --> 00:12:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei! Me next!</font>

199
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll get your turn.</font>

200
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw. It fell almost instantly again.</font>

201
00:12:42,930 --> 00:12:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin's paper airplane flies the farthest.</font>

202
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What makes it any different from ours?</font>

203
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gotta be something with his brain.</font>

204
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys are folding it wrong.</font>

205
00:12:56,400 --> 00:13:00,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish all of ours 
could fly far together.</font>

206
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, fine. 
I'll show you how it's done.</font>

207
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho, come here.</font>

208
00:13:14,730 --> 00:13:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lucky us!</font>

209
00:13:16,090 --> 00:13:17,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Shin!</font>

210
00:13:17,860 --> 00:13:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

211
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pay attention.</font>

212
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use the center fold line to fold 
the left and right sides symmetrically.</font>

213
00:13:26,090 --> 00:13:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you raise the angle 
of the wings up a little.</font>

214
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it!</font>

215
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Let's fly them all together!</font>

216
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Kay!</font>

217
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All together!</font>

218
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:50,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

219
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:51,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it!</font>

220
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice!</font>

221
00:13:53,410 --> 00:13:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then, I thought all of us 
could fly anywhere together forever.</i></font>

222
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

223
00:14:05,530 --> 00:14:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Cool!</font>

224
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The things you do don't change 
even when you're an adult, Shin.</font>

225
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

226
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:32,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we fly them at the same time,</font>

227
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they each end up going 
in different directions.</font>

228
00:14:36,730 --> 00:14:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the past, I clearly knew 
what path I wanted to take.</font>

229
00:14:41,090 --> 00:14:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no worries.</font>

230
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't say the same 
now that I'm an adult.</font>

231
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen?</font>

232
00:14:53,690 --> 00:14:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's the time to choose 
what I'm going to specialize in.</font>

233
00:14:57,470 --> 00:15:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more things I know, 
the more possibilities I can see.</font>

234
00:15:17,130 --> 00:15:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what path you take, 
I'm sure you'll do fine, Shin.</font>

235
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be cheering you on.</font>

236
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Thanks.</font>

237
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wow, way to go, Shin-chan.</i></font>

238
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Shin seemed really
confident last night.</font>

239
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course he is.</font>

240
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's handsome, a doctor,</font>

241
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and on top of that, 
he saved Mizuho's dad's life.</font>

242
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, on the other hand, are a nobody. 
You're an unemployed swimmer.</font>

243
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any normal girl wouldn't choose you.</font>

244
00:15:58,400 --> 00:16:01,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you say one good thing about me?</font>

245
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well... How about this?</i></font>

246
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fact you can tackle things 
straight on without a thought.</i></font>

247
00:16:08,560 --> 00:16:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like that's not a compliment.</font>

248
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's totally a compliment.</font>

249
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, just do your best, buddy.</font>

250
00:16:16,270 --> 00:16:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah. I'll contact you again later.</i></font>

251
00:16:20,290 --> 00:16:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki... Hurry up and open your eyes.</font>

252
00:16:27,690 --> 00:16:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

253
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I lost to that straightforward 
personality of yours.</font>

254
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if that's everything?</font>

255
00:16:40,770 --> 00:16:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This too, Mizuho.</font>

256
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:45,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought things that could 
be useful for the bathroom.</font>

257
00:16:45,690 --> 00:16:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. You're a great help!</font>

258
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's get going.</font>

259
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

260
00:16:59,550 --> 00:17:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A photo?</font>

261
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:02,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure your dad will like that.</font>

262
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. He won't be lonely 
if Mom's with him.</font>

263
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you.</font>

264
00:17:15,970 --> 00:17:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Do you remember that card?</font>

265
00:17:18,840 --> 00:17:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

266
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you got rid of yours.</font>

267
00:17:22,530 --> 00:17:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know about that.</font>

268
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an illustration card 
I made for the Ao High festival.</font>

269
00:17:29,300 --> 00:17:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You helped me a ton 
during those times, too.</font>

270
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you worked so hard, we were 
able to make precious memories.</font>

271
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really grateful for that.</font>

272
00:17:39,890 --> 00:17:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all worked hard for that.</font>

273
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose.</font>

274
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:48,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get going, Mizuho.</font>

275
00:17:48,470 --> 00:17:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

276
00:17:51,580 --> 00:17:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So pretty...</font>

277
00:17:56,690 --> 00:17:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seeing the ocean really calms me.</font>

278
00:17:59,390 --> 00:18:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

279
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been thinking a lot 
about you lately, Shin.</font>

280
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:08,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to thank you properly.</font>

281
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just about my dad, but also 
how you've supported me all this time.</font>

282
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin, I...</font>

283
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That card.</font>

284
00:18:18,090 --> 00:18:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

285
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even to this day, it's displayed 
in my locker at the hospital.</font>

286
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That day, being in the classroom
 with you, Mizuho...</font>

287
00:18:29,530 --> 00:18:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Shin.</font>

288
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's remember this moment forever.</font>

289
00:18:35,850 --> 00:18:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">September 18th. 5:20 PM.</font>

290
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin and I were in an Ao High classroom.</font>

291
00:18:50,570 --> 00:18:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold onto that card 
as a reminder of today.</font>

292
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

293
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a precious memory of mine.</font>

294
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think you'd cherish it so much.</font>

295
00:19:10,060 --> 00:19:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we were students, 
I watched over you and your studies.</font>

296
00:19:14,770 --> 00:19:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At first, I thought it was just something 
for my own satisfaction. But...</font>

297
00:19:19,370 --> 00:19:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I went to Ao High.</font>

298
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing, Shin.</font>

299
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You actually became student 
council president, too.</font>

300
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it yourself:</font>

301
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Shin would be 
the student council president."</font>

302
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

303
00:19:32,990 --> 00:19:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that from when we all 
celebrated getting into Ao High?</font>

304
00:19:37,940 --> 00:19:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bows on Ao High's 
uniforms were so cute!</font>

305
00:19:41,260 --> 00:19:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you joining the swim club, Kizuki?</font>

306
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. What'll you do, Shin?</font>

307
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Me? Hmm...</font>

308
00:19:49,260 --> 00:19:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about student council president?</font>

309
00:19:50,770 --> 00:19:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, right! Nice one, Mizuho.</font>

310
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have time for that.</font>

311
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go again with that. 
You're such a boring guy.</font>

312
00:19:58,970 --> 00:20:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon! Live a little!</font>

313
00:20:00,860 --> 00:20:02,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho, Kizuki!</font>

314
00:20:02,320 --> 00:20:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold onto Shin's legs!</font>

315
00:20:04,970 --> 00:20:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger that!</font>

316
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alley oop!</font>

317
00:20:10,970 --> 00:20:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you guys doing?</font>

318
00:20:14,700 --> 00:20:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're soaked!</font>

319
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I'm talking about!</font>

320
00:20:17,990 --> 00:20:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now <i>this</i> is adolescence!</font>

321
00:20:20,330 --> 00:20:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Shin.</font>

322
00:20:26,250 --> 00:20:31,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just happy that 
I could be with you again.</font>

323
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for back then.</font>

324
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd just been rejected
from your #1 choice school,</font>

325
00:20:41,860 --> 00:20:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet I said I was so happy.</font>

326
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:45,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about it. 
Plus, I wasn't rejected.</font>

327
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

328
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:50,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to be with you and everyone 
else. So I pretended I failed.</font>

329
00:20:50,670 --> 00:20:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! You turned down 
<i>the</i> Seikai High School?!</font>

330
00:20:54,530 --> 00:20:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My life's always been 
guided by you, Mizuho.</font>

331
00:20:58,370 --> 00:20:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By me?</font>

332
00:21:01,090 --> 00:21:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you lost your mother...</font>

333
00:21:03,790 --> 00:21:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You looked like you 
were in so much pain...</font>

334
00:21:06,290 --> 00:21:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't want you to make 
that face ever again.</font>

335
00:21:09,850 --> 00:21:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">I wanted to be someone who could save 
the lives of the people in your life.</font></font>

336
00:21:15,990 --> 00:21:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize... Even though 
I've been by your side this whole time.</font>

337
00:21:20,780 --> 00:21:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can do anything for you.</font>

338
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember what I told you when 
we went on that gondola together?</font>

339
00:21:38,180 --> 00:21:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already set my heart 
on being with you.</font>

340
00:21:43,820 --> 00:21:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So when you're ready too, tell me.</font>

341
00:21:49,580 --> 00:21:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I was really surprised.</font>

342
00:21:53,210 --> 00:21:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even when I knew about 
Kizuki's feelings for you...</font>

343
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when you two started dating...</font>

344
00:22:00,810 --> 00:22:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've decided to go out with Kizuki.</font>

345
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't give up on you, Mizuho.</font>

346
00:22:09,140 --> 00:22:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't imagine a life without you.</font>

347
00:22:12,470 --> 00:22:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you, Mizuho.</font>

348
00:22:14,530 --> 00:22:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I live for you, and want to 
keep living for you.</font>

349
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be happy with you.</font>

350
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you marry me?</font>

351
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:46,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10"><font color="#57b3c9"><b>Translation:
Timing:
Editing and Typesetting:
Quality Control:
Translation Check:</b></font></font></font></font>

352
